{
  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b Fix react-is version mismatch causing useLayoutEffect error (#446)\n\nThe react-is package was at version 19.x while react/react-dom are at 18.x,\ncausing @dnd-kit to fail with \"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading\n'useLayoutEffect')\" error.\n\nDowngrading react-is to 18.3.1 to match React version.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
